## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="b0bb4-102">W poniższej tabeli przedstawiono aktualnie obsługiwane opcje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b0bb4-102">The following table shows the currently supported options.</span></span>  
  
|<span data-ttu-id="b0bb4-103">Kategoria</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b0bb4-103">Category</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="b0bb4-104">Ustawienie</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b0bb4-104">Setting</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="b0bb4-105">Wartość/efekt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b0bb4-105">Value/effect</span></span>|  
|--------------|-------------|-------------------|  
|<span data-ttu-id="b0bb4-106">przedsiębiorc</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b0bb4-106">contract</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="b0bb4-107">dziedziczenie</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b0bb4-107">inheritance</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="b0bb4-108">`true`Aby włączyć dziedziczenie kontraktu; `false` , aby go wyłączyć.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b0bb4-108">`true` to turn contract inheritance on; `false` to turn it off.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="b0bb4-109">Wartość domyślna to `true`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b0bb4-109">The default is `true`.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="b0bb4-110">środowisko uruchomieniowe</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b0bb4-110">runtime</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="b0bb4-111">sprawdzanie</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b0bb4-111">checking</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="b0bb4-112">`true`Aby włączyć sprawdzanie czasu wykonywania; `false` , aby go wyłączyć.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b0bb4-112">`true` to turn run-time checking on; `false` to turn it off.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b0bb4-113">Wartość domyślna to `true`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b0bb4-113">The default is `true`.</span></span>|  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b0bb4-114">Tego atrybutu można użyć, jak pokazano w poniższych przykładach.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b0bb4-114">You can use this attribute as illustrated in the following examples.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b0bb4-115">Aby wyłączyć sprawdzanie w czasie wykonywania dla całego zestawu:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b0bb4-115">To turn off run-time checking for the entire assembly:</span></span>  
  
```  
[assembly:ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b0bb4-116">Aby włączyć sprawdzanie kontraktu w czasie wykonywania dla określonego typu:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b0bb4-116">To turn run-time contract checking on for a specific type:</span></span>  
  
```  
   [ContractOption("runtime", "checking", true)]  
   class TypeWithRuntimeChecking {  
  
       ...  
  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b0bb4-117">Aby włączyć sprawdzanie w czasie wykonywania dla określonej metody:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b0bb4-117">To turn run-time checking off for a specific method:</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Turn off all contract inheritance from interface IList<T>  
[ContractOption("contract", "inheritance", false)]  
class MyConcurrentList<T> : IList<T> {  
   ...  
}  
  
[ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
public override MyMethod(int x) {  
   // no inherited contracts checked at runtime,  
   // no invariants checked at runtime.  
   ...  
}  
  
       [ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
       public void MethodWithoutRuntimeChecking(...) {  
          ...  
       }  
   }  
  
```
